snippet.title: Adrian's Digital Basement
snippet.description:
Welcome to Adrian's Digital Basement. I love old computers! If you do too, this channel is for you! This channel is just a result of my hobby, so please be kind when my production quality doesn't stand up to those of other full time content producers. 

If you are interested in sending in a donation to the channel, please contact me via email. You can find my email address below under "Business Inquiries." (Visible on YouTube via a web browser, not the phone app.)
